data.description: Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom abode boasts fantastic flooring and a charming fireplace, setting the stage for cozy nights in. Outside, the expansive backyard beckons for leisurely afternoons or lively gatherings. With a convenient 2-car garage, this home is primed for homeowners seeking a welcoming space to call their own and it is priced to move. It also features solar panels that will save you plenty on your electric bill.
